1. You can participate in this activity with GXC, the minimum starting amount is 20 GXC;
2. If you are participating in a current product, your profits will be distributed after you quit the activity, and the platform will charge 10% of your profits as the management fees; if you are participating in a fixed-cycle product, your profits will be distributed after the event expires, the account is unified and the platform will also charge 10% of your profits as the management fee;
3. All products in this mining pool have an exit period of 3 days and no profit during the exit period; fixed-cycle products, withdrawn from the middle, the proceeds you receive will be calculated based on current profits; however, if you are participating 180-day product, you cannot quit from the middle.
4. The historical reference annualized rate of return is 2~9% (for reference only), and your final profits are based on the actual node operating profits;

